{"tid":1947344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記者問柒婆:Playgroup係咪豁免於新措施? 柒婆答：咩係Playgroup?","createTime":"2020-03-28T08:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T12:48:04.000Z","uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7477c590e48b947409e42e9e8862db47d11165fe","tid":1947344,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wn87Jie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWn87Jie.png&h=6cd71b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥宣布周日起禁止多於 4 人在公眾地方群組聚集，<br />\n記者問到 playgroup 是否在豁免範圍，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥反問「咩叫 playgroup？細路仔玩嗰啲？」</span><br />\n她續指，完全不鼓勵這類場所繼續營運，尤其讓小朋友聚集，<br />\nplaygroup 並不豁免於相關措施，多於 4 人的聚集亦會被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89838155bbaf1fc86edf59f1cbc389ef74c77a1b","tid":1947344,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"某程度黎講的確係細路仔玩嗰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff9b137222ad8e5a65e6930e03bb3f2055e3778","tid":1947344,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"你老母個西呀"},{"pid":"a398b6a05607c8f363cc40ad4b867ab1c114e1a3","tid":1947344,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大人都有playgroup<br />\n問清楚好d"}]}